info.title: Schema of Redis Cache events published to Azure Event Grid
info.description: Describes the schema of the Redis Cache events published to Azure Event Grid. This corresponds to the Data property of an EventGridEvent.

RedisPatchingCompletedEventData.description: Schema of the Data property of an EventGridEvent for an Microsoft.Cache.PatchingCompleted event.

timestamp.description: The time at which the event occurred.

status.description: The status of this event. Failed or  succeeded

RedisScalingCompletedEventData.description: Schema of the Data property of an EventGridEvent for an Microsoft.Cache.ScalingCompleted event.

timestamp.description: The time at which the event occurred.

status.description: The status of this event. Failed or  succeeded

timestamp.description: The time at which the event occurred.

status.description: The status of this event. Failed or  succeeded
